Different: On Monday the Dallas Buyers Club actress looked surprised as she left a workout






The actress has handled their split with incredible grace, choosing to not cast her man in a bad light after it was claimed in July he had gotten intimate with their children's nanny.Instead, she has put on a united front with the Oscar winner and has been focusing on her family as the exes have headed to therapy and attended church together.In late October she and Ben were seen side-by-side in a car as they headed to a grocery store near their respective homes in the Pacific Palisades.Meanwhile, Ben has been filming Live By Night in Brunswick, Georgia.  





